##### Grant ReadOnly privileges ######

GRANT CONNECT ON DATABASE bbname TO user;

GRANT USAGE ON SCHEMA public TO user;
GRANT USAGE ON SCHEMA privatetable TO user;

GRANT SELECT ON ALL TABLES IN SCHEMA public TO user;
GRANT SELECT ON ALL TABLES IN SCHEMA privatetable TO user;


GRANT SELECT ON ALL SEQUENCES IN SCHEMA public TO user;
GRANT SELECT ON ALL SEQUENCES IN SCHEMA privatetable TO user;



##### Grant ReadWrite user ##########
GRANT CONNECT ON DATABASE dbname TO user;

GRANT USAGE ON SCHEMA public TO user;
GRANT USAGE ON SCHEMA privatetable TO user;


GRANT SELECT, INSERT, UPDATE, DELETE ON ALL TABLES IN SCHEMA public TO write_user_uat;
GRANT SELECT, INSERT, UPDATE, DELETE ON ALL TABLES IN SCHEMA privatetable TO user;


GRANT SELECT ON ALL SEQUENCES IN SCHEMA public TO user;
GRANT SELECT ON ALL SEQUENCES IN SCHEMA privatetable TO user;



